Killer Peruvian chicken - perhaps the  most juicy and flavorful Peruvian chicken I've had.  After a long search for the best Peruvian chicken in the area this may be it.  Fried yuca is tip top, good platanos, and the side salad is the best you'll find at any chicken shop.  Also recommend the chicken gyro here.
